oin volume for the 2nd straight quarter (ETH 22% of volume vs BTC at 19%). We are starting to see a shift.”</blockquote>', 'Ecommerce Giant JD.com Accepts China’s Digital Yuan as Payments on Singles Day Shopping Fest', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-26 03:49:07', '2021-11-26 03:49:07', '', 1, 'http://localhost/wp/vt-ventures/?p=866', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
